<h1 id="push-notifications">Push notifications</h1>

<p>In order to get push notifications on your app working you need to do as follows:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Go to the Google Console https://console.developers.google.com</li>
  <li>Create a new project / open project</li>
  <li>Click on ‘APIs &amp; Auth’ on the left</li>
  <li>Find the ‘Google Cloud Messaging for Android’ option, and press off to turn it on</li>
  <li>Go to the creditials tab on the left</li>
  <li>Go the ‘Public API access’ section and click ‘Create new key’</li>
  <li>Choose ‘Server key’ and click ‘Create’</li>
  <li>The API key is now shown under the section ‘Key for server applications’</li>
  <li>Go to your site panel, copy the key in General-&gt;Settings-&gt;Google Cloud Messaging</li>
</ul>

